<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-20 text-center">
  <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Build habits that stick.</h1>
  <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
    Rootein helps you track daily habits with a simple calendar.
    Check off each day, build streaks, and watch consistency compound.
  </p>

  <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 mb-16">
    <%= link_to "Get Started", new_registration_path, class: "bg-green-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-green-700" %>
    <%= link_to "Log In", new_session_path, class: "border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-50" %>
  </div>

  <!-- Feature highlights -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-green-700">Track Daily</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">Simple calendar view. Click a day to mark it done. Green means you showed up.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-green-700">Build Streaks</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">See your current streak count. The longer the chain, the harder it is to break.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-green-700">Stay Accountable</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">Get email reminders when you're slacking. Gentle nudges to keep you on track.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="mt-16 text-sm text-gray-400">Originally built in 2009. Rebuilt with Rails 8.</p>
</div>
